        "TradeItemDescriptionInformation": {
          "AdditionalTradeItemDescription": [
            {
              "LanguageCode": "en",
              "Value": "NPWT silicone foam dressing consists of silicone foam dressing attached with a suction bell and fixations film strips. \nThe silicone foam dressing is comprised of Polyurethane (PU) film, three-layer pad comprised of PU foam, Polyacrylic acid absorbent fibre and Polyester fabric, the pad and the PU film are coated with silicone adhesive, and polyethylene (PE) release liners. The PE liners are removed when the dressing is applied to the wound bed. \nThe suction bell is comprised of a polyvinyl chloride drainage tubing with a polypropylene (PP) pinch clamp, a polypropylene luer taper, a bell shape dome made of  polyvinyl chloride (PVC), a transparent polyurethane film coated with acrylic adhesive. The suction bell is attached on the silicone foam dressing surface. \nFixations film strips is composed of PU film coated with acrylic adhesive and PE release liners. The PE release liners are removed when the strips are applied onto the silicone foam dressing.                                                                   size:12.5cm x 40cm"
            }
          ],
